reviews.text: Already crowded at 8am, the service is fine and the wait time is pretty short. They serve the food unexpectedly fast and it tasted decent. The shredded albalone and ham macaroni that I got was well flavoured. The toast and egg was good and the milk tea was very rich in flavours. The price is only around 35$ for a meal and the portion is decent enough

reviews.text: Already crowded at 8am, the service is fine and the wait time is pretty short. They serve the food unexpectedly fast and it tasted decent. The shredded albalone and ham macaroni that I got was well flavoured. The toast and egg was good and the milk tea was very rich in flavours. The price is only around 35$ for a meal and the portion is decent enough

首先，杯凍檸茶真係好飲，the iced lemon tea is great.
今日係食早餐，都係普通港式早餐，無特別好又無特別差。
The Hong Kong style breakfast is ok.
唯一一個原因會吸引我回來就係杯凍檸茶。The iced lemon tea is the only reason for me to come here again.
脆炸鷄肶公仔麵頂好味，奶茶好飲。不防來試下啦～😋👍
一所頗有懷舊色彩的茶餐廳，店內裝修富有濃烈的懷舊裝潢，乾淨企理，下午茶必食雞脾湯即食麵，雞脾炸到火喉剛剛好，皮脆肉嫩多汁，絕對無得輸，真的是必食推介！

木澤超人：一間主打懷舊主題的茶餐廳，先講價錢，比起同區茶記算不上平，食品方面企理（早餐）而定必要試茶走（奶茶加煉奶）好滑溜👍🏻，店內格局好像7-8十年代茶餐廳風格可算是香港特色！難怪有不少旅遊客光顧（可能旁邊就是黃大仙廟吧）！
來香港旅遊的朋友們，如果您們會去黃大仙廟參觀，我「木澤超人」推介您們可以過來試一試，感受一下香港風格茶餐廳吧

not a bad neighborhood mall. small like all in hk, but vibrant
Big shopping mall in Wong Tai Sin. Lots of good restaurant choices. Clean public bathrooms.
There is an access to the small shopping mall through Exit D of the Wong Tai Sin MTR Station. Many restaurants and food kiosks line the passage way.
The shops here are smaller than those in the north mall.
